ZH: 选举是每个民主社会的重要组成部分。
EN: Elections are an important part of every democratic society.

ZH: 明天将举行市长选举。
EN: The mayoral election will be held tomorrow.

ZH: 在选举中，每个公民都有平等的投票权。
EN: In elections, every citizen has an equal right to vote.

ZH: 我们应该积极参与选举过程。
EN: We should actively participate in the election process.

ZH: 这次选举是历史性的。
EN: This election is historic.

ZH: 公平的选举是民主制度的基础。
EN: Fair elections are the foundation of a democratic system.

ZH: 他在选举中获得了大多数选票。
EN: He won the majority of votes in the election.

ZH: 她是这次选举的主要候选人之一。
EN: She is one of the primary candidates in this election.

ZH: 选举结果将在下个星期宣布。
EN: The election results will be announced next week.

ZH: 大家都在等待选举的结果。
EN: Everyone is waiting for the election results.

ZH: 我们需要确保选举是公正合法的。
EN: We need to ensure that the election is fair and legal.

ZH: 这次选举的投票率非常低。
EN: The voter turnout for this election is very low.

ZH: 她赢得了竞选市议员的选举。
EN: She won the election for city councilor.

ZH: 这次选举对国家的未来至关重要。
EN: This election is crucial for the future of the country.

ZH: 选举由选民决定。
EN: Elections are decided by the voters.

ZH: 候选人们都在为选举做准备。
EN: The candidates are all preparing for the election.

ZH: 这场选举将决定我们的未来。
EN: This election will determine our future.

ZH: 全国选举将在明年举行。
EN: The national election will be held next year.

ZH: 这次选举将改变我们的政治景观。
EN: This election will change our political landscape.
